<div class="solution-begin"><button id='sol-start-2' class="jk-circle-right solution-icon clickable" onclick="toggle_visibility('sol-body-2', 'sol-start-2')">  Solution </button></div><div class="solution-body" id = "sol-body-2" style="display: none;">


You can use "pointranges", or "line" and "ribbon".  
`stat_summary` will take the data and for each value of `x` calculate some function (in this case the mean, or the mean and SE):  



